original_title: Anura Kumara secures win in Kandy
original_body_lines: The results of the Kandy polling division in Kandy District for the 2024 Presidential Election have been released by the Election Commission.
National People’s Power (NPP) candidate Anura Kumara Dissanayake has received the highest number of votes in the Beliatta polling division with a total of 13,336 votes.
